 host-parasite interactions and disease emergence.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Dietrich, Muriel", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Wilkinson, David A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Benlali, Aude", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lagadec, Erwan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ramasindrazana, Beza", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Dellagi, Koussay", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Tortosa, Pablo", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["*Leptospira", "Animals", "Chiroptera/*microbiology/virology", "Coinfection", "Leptospirosis/microbiology/*transmission/*veterinary", "Paramyxoviridae Infections/*transmission/*veterinary/virology", "Paramyxoviridae/genetics", "Population Dynamics", "Seasons", "Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/bb04d0f50ebbaad8cff085793454e180", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/29c74f17a7cd1d800758260b8d7577cba75b174572030ceae94942b938add739", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/ZVHGB5KV", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/ZVHGB5KV", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/0bcdc7ece3807a0ee1c196f797862625!/b96096-98425", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/26f7ce5dd404e33c6570edd4ba250d20", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "11", "pages": "4280-4289", "title": "Environmental Microbiology", "volume": "17"}, "alte